cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.MM

The paper deals with video prediction using machine learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The approach also involves reasoning about interactions between entities, which suggests the use of techniques from machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of latent variables, which is a common technique in robotics (cs.RO) and multimedia (cs.MM) research. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.CV, cs.LG, and cs.AI, followed by cs.RO and cs.MM.
